data.text: @michael_hoerger @DrMoPPC So many mixed emotions around the #covid19shot -Hoping for an end to the tragedies and suffering this virus has caused.  Realistic though that it won’t end soon enough. Sad for people who have died.  Grateful to have life and the opportunity for the vaccine #thisisourshot #hapc
@michael_hoerger @SoniaMKhunkhun Wooohoooo I had tears of joy!!!! So grateful!!! My heart is full.
